### 20.1 创建 API Key 流程

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户
    participant UI as 控制台前端
    participant GW as 网关API
    participant AUTH as 鉴权服务
    participant BILL as 配额/计费服务
    participant LOG as 审计日志

    U->>UI: 点击“新建API Key”并提交表单
